{"tid":1347244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗市民：周六晚已收到村長通知提醒勿外出","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T05:46:22.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f1deb301895cfb2a597ab3c2ad492d9b30114e8b","tid":1347244,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:42:19.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】星期日晚元朗西鐵站爆發衝突，有市民在本台節目時事全方位表示，星期六晚已收到村長通知提醒不要外出，亦有市民不滿西鐵站暫停服務的安排。<br />\n<br />\n早上元朗西鐵站在月台的港鐵職員比平日增多，亦有特別穿橙衣的職員觀察有否突發情況，站內數部閘機損毀，暫停使用，期間有市民指摘警方無盡力保護市民。<br />\n<br />\n有居住在元朗的居民在本台節目時事全方位上表示，前日收到村長通知，指星期日盡量不要外出以免打錯人。有市民質疑西鐵站暫停服務的安排。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵解釋並無刻意讓白衣人進入車廂，但當時車門被卡着，又有人按緊急掣，情況非常混亂，當車長報告有人打鬥，港鐵已安排列車駛走。"},{"pid":"9d3b614ccd27fa3dac6121f11ca56dd21794f97a","tid":1347244,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:42:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SQUr1Fmwn1M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSQUr1Fmwn1M&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhHy9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=2ffef6f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SQUr1Fmwn1M</a>"},{"pid":"e9f0e372b958b097f02c54ff7d6d5f1b97831627","tid":1347244,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:42:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=356270\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356270&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhHy9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=ce2cf085\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356270&h=2f59100e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=356270</a>"},{"pid":"398e22f8a8f1c93fa6d514860e81c869631b8cb2","tid":1347244,"uid":224066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:43:42.000Z","msg":"董建華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed1782287a97a5201fb